snippet.title: Amber Heard Travels Solo After Met Gala Appearance Without Johnny
snippet.description:
Friday, May 6, 2016 - Amber Heard is a dame in denim arriving in Los Angeles. The actress made a stunning appearance at the Met Gala Monday night but did not bring husband Johnny Depp along. She returns to Los Angeles solo.
